name: MGJ6D1215040MC
series_description: Offering dual output voltages of +18V/-2.5V for Rohm devices & +15V/-4V for Wolfspeed devices, the MGJ6D series DC-DC converter is ideal for powering ‘high side’ and ‘low side’ gate drive circuits for Silicon Carbide Mosfets in bridge circuits. A choice of asymmetric output voltages allows optimum drive levels for best system efficiency and EMI. The MGJ6D series is characterised for high isolation and dv/dt requirements commonly seen in bridge circuits used in motor drives and inverters. A disable/frequency synchronization pin simplifies EMC filter design. The MGJ6D series protection features include short circuit protection and overload protection.
